(3, 80, 'Angola capta 3,4 mil milhões USD em investimentos nos últimos três anos', 'angola-capta-3-4-mil-milhoes-usd-em-investimentos-nos-ultimos-tres-anos', '{\"en\":\"\",\"hr\":\"\",\"pt-br\":\"Angola capta 3,4 mil milh\\u00f5es USD em investimentos nos \\u00faltimos tr\\u00eas anos\"}', '{\"en\":\"\",\"hr\":\"\",\"pt-br\":\"Dados pela Ag\\u00eancia de Investimento Privado e Promo\\u00e7\\u00e3o das Exporta\\u00e7\\u00f5es (AIPEX) apresentam 345 projectos com realce para os aplicados \\u00e0 ind\\u00fastria transformadora\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p><br><\\/p>\",\"hr\":\"<p><br><\\/p>\",\"pt-br\":\"<p>A Ag\\u00eancia de Investimento Privado e Promo\\u00e7\\u00e3o das Exporta\\u00e7\\u00f5es (AIPEX) registou, nos \\u00faltimos tr\\u00eas anos, um total de 345 projectos, avaliados em 3,4 mil milh\\u00f5es de d\\u00f3lares, divididos em v\\u00e1rios sectores de actividade, com destaque para a ind\\u00fastria transformadora, que com 153 projectos representa 1,7 mil milh\\u00f5es de d\\u00f3lares, de acordo com o <em>Jornal de Angola<\\/em>.<\\/p><p>O presidente do Conselho de Administra\\u00e7\\u00e3o da AIPEX, Ant\\u00f3nio Henriques da Silva, que fazia o balan\\u00e7o de tr\\u00eas anos de actividade da Ag\\u00eancia, acrescentou que logo a seguir receberam o maior volume de investimentos os sectores de presta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de servi\\u00e7os, com 69 projectos e 313 milh\\u00f5es de d\\u00f3lares, da Agricultura, com 16 projectos e 213 milh\\u00f5es de d\\u00f3lares e do Com\\u00e9rcio, com 78 projectos e 149 milh\\u00f5es de d\\u00f3lares. \\u201cSe forem implementados nos termos dos registos efectuados, os projectos poder\\u00e3o criar 24.987 postos de trabalho directos, 23.191 dos quais para m\\u00e3o-de-obra local e apenas 1.796 para expatriados\\u201d, declarou. Luanda continua a ser o destino preferencial dos investimentos, com cerca de 79% das propostas, seguindo-se as prov\\u00edncias do Bengo (13%), Benguela (12%) e Malanje (10%).<\\/p>\"}', 'assets/embaixada/img/paginas/d2bf33acbb440778caa859d20d00f20d44f145c9.jpg', 'pt-br', '2021-03-25 19:51:25', '2021-03-26 00:11:20', '1'),
(4, 80, 'Hungria apoia Angola no combate à criminalidade', 'hungria-apoia-angola-no-combate-a-criminalidade', '{\"en\":\"PARLIAMENT APPROVES COOPERATION AGREEMENT\",\"hr\":\"A Parlament j\\u00f3v\\u00e1hagyja meg\\u00e1llapod\\u00e1st\",\"pt-br\":\"Parlamento aprova acordo de coopera\\u00e7\\u00e3o bilateral\"}', '{\"en\":\"Hungary supports Angola in fighting crime\",\"hr\":\"Magyarorsz\\u00e1g t\\u00e1mogatja Angol\\u00e1t a b\\u0171n\\u00f6z\\u00e9s elleni k\\u00fczdelemben\",\"pt-br\":\"Hungria apoia Angola no combate \\u00e0 criminalidade em todas as suas formas e manifesta\\u00e7\\u00f5es.\"}', '{\"en\":\"<pre class=\\\"ql-syntax\\\" spellcheck=\\\"false\\\">The National Assembly approved on Monday (26) the Cooperation Agreement between the Republic of Angola and Hungary in Matters of Security and Public Order, whose signature between the two states dates back to February 25, 2020, in Budapest.\\nThe Secretary of State of the External Relations for International Cooperation and Angolan Communities added that cooperation is essentially aimed at exchanging experiences and improving the level of internal organisation, taking into account the benefits that Hungary can offer in the field of prevention and fighting crime in all its forms and manifestations.\\nThe cooperation, continued Domingos Vieira Lopes, cited by Jornal de Angola, covers the areas of fighting against terrorism, illegal immigration, corruption, money laundering, extending to the staff training, supply of equipment and enshrines the provision of mutual assistance on the matters provided for in the agreement, with emphasis on criminal investigation.\\nAccording to that head of Ministry of External Relations, the signing of this legal instrument is part of the search for diversification of partnerships in order to achieve and improve the best ways, practices and procedures in the prevention and fighting against several type of crimes. The agreement, he said, will allow the parties to reinforce cooperation in the field of public order and security, as well as enhance the different central executive organs and services of the Ministry of Interior with more strength in this area that will serve to improve the exercise of daily activity in order to raise the quality of the public service provided to citizens.\\n| Source: Jornal de Angola, 27th April edition\\n\\n\\n\\n<\\/pre><p><br><\\/p>\",\"hr\":\"<p>Az Orsz\\u00e1ggy\\u0171l\\u00e9s h\\u00e9tf\\u0151n (26) j\\u00f3v\\u00e1hagyta az Angolai K\\u00f6zt\\u00e1rsas\\u00e1g \\u00e9s Magyarorsz\\u00e1g k\\u00f6z\\u00f6tti biztons\\u00e1gi \\u00e9s k\\u00f6zrendv\\u00e9delmi egy\\u00fcttm\\u0171k\\u00f6d\\u00e9si meg\\u00e1llapod\\u00e1st, amelynek al\\u00e1\\u00edr\\u00e1sa a k\\u00e9t \\u00e1llam k\\u00f6z\\u00f6tt 2020. febru\\u00e1r 25-ig ny\\u00falik vissza Budapesten.<\\/p><p>A nemzetk\\u00f6zi egy\\u00fcttm\\u0171k\\u00f6d\\u00e9s\\u00e9rt \\u00e9s az angolai k\\u00f6z\\u00f6ss\\u00e9gek\\u00e9rt felel\\u0151s k\\u00fcl\\u00fcgyminiszter hozz\\u00e1tette, hogy az egy\\u00fcttm\\u0171k\\u00f6d\\u00e9s alapvet\\u0151en a tapasztalatcser\\u00e9re \\u00e9s a bels\\u0151 szervezetts\\u00e9g jav\\u00edt\\u00e1s\\u00e1ra ir\\u00e1nyul, figyelembe v\\u00e9ve azokat az el\\u0151ny\\u00f6ket, amelyeket Magyarorsz\\u00e1g a b\\u0171nmegel\\u0151z\\u00e9s \\u00e9s a b\\u0171n\\u00f6z\\u00e9s elleni k\\u00fczdelem ter\\u00fclet\\u00e9n k\\u00edn\\u00e1lhat minden ter\\u00fclet\\u00e9n. form\\u00e1k \\u00e9s megnyilv\\u00e1nul\\u00e1sok.<\\/p><p>Egy\\u00fcttm\\u0171k\\u00f6d\\u00e9s, folytatta Domingos Vieira Lopes, id\\u00e9zi Jornal de Angola, a terrorizmus, az illeg\\u00e1lis bev\\u00e1ndorl\\u00e1s, a korrupci\\u00f3, a p\\u00e9nzmos\\u00e1s elleni k\\u00fczdelem ter\\u00fcleteire terjed ki, kiterjesztve a szem\\u00e9lyzet k\\u00e9pz\\u00e9s\\u00e9re, a felszerel\\u00e9sell\\u00e1t\\u00e1sra, \\u00e9s r\\u00f6gz\\u00edti a k\\u00f6lcs\\u00f6n\\u00f6s seg\\u00edts\\u00e9gny\\u00fajt\\u00e1st a meg\\u00e1llapod\\u00e1sban el\\u0151\\u00edrt k\\u00e9rd\\u00e9sekben. , k\\u00fcl\\u00f6n\\u00f6s tekintettel a b\\u0171n\\u00fcgyi nyomoz\\u00e1sra.<\\/p><p>A MIREX vezet\\u0151je szerint ennek a jogi eszk\\u00f6znek az al\\u00e1\\u00edr\\u00e1sa a partners\\u00e9gek diverzifik\\u00e1ci\\u00f3j\\u00e1nak felkutat\\u00e1s\\u00e1nak r\\u00e9sze, annak \\u00e9rdek\\u00e9ben, hogy a k\\u00fcl\\u00f6nb\\u00f6z\\u0151 b\\u0171ncselekm\\u00e9nyek megel\\u0151z\\u00e9s\\u00e9ben \\u00e9s elleni k\\u00fczdelemben a legjobb m\\u00f3dszereket, gyakorlatokat \\u00e9s elj\\u00e1r\\u00e1sokat \\u00e9rj\\u00e9k el \\u00e9s jav\\u00edts\\u00e1k. A meg\\u00e1llapod\\u00e1s szerinte lehet\\u0151v\\u00e9 teszi a felek sz\\u00e1m\\u00e1ra, hogy meger\\u0151s\\u00edts\\u00e9k az egy\\u00fcttm\\u0171k\\u00f6d\\u00e9st a biztons\\u00e1g \\u00e9s a k\\u00f6zrend ter\\u00fclet\\u00e9n, valamint a Bel\\u00fcgyminiszt\\u00e9rium k\\u00fcl\\u00f6nb\\u00f6z\\u0151 k\\u00f6zponti v\\u00e9grehajt\\u00f3 szerveit \\u00e9s szolg\\u00e1latait nagyobb er\\u0151vel er\\u0151s\\u00edts\\u00e9k ezen a ter\\u00fcleten, amelyek javul\\u00e1st fognak szolg\\u00e1lni. a mindennapi tev\\u00e9kenys\\u00e9g gyakorl\\u00e1sa a polg\\u00e1rok sz\\u00e1m\\u00e1ra ny\\u00fajtott k\\u00f6zszolg\\u00e1ltat\\u00e1sok min\\u0151s\\u00e9g\\u00e9nek jav\\u00edt\\u00e1sa \\u00e9rdek\\u00e9ben.<\\/p><p><strong>Forr\\u00e1s: Jornal de Angola, \\u00e1prilis 27-i kiad\\u00e1s<\\/strong><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\",\"pt-br\":\"<p class=\\\"ql-align-justify\\\">A Assembleia Nacional aprovou, na segunda-feira (26), o Acordo de Coopera\\u00e7\\u00e3o entre a Rep\\u00fablica de Angola e a Hungria em Mat\\u00e9ria de Seguran\\u00e7a e Ordem P\\u00fablica, cuja assinatura entre os dois Estados remonta a 25 de Fevereiro de 2020, em Budapeste.<\\/p><p class=\\\"ql-align-justify\\\">O secret\\u00e1rio de Estado das Rela\\u00e7\\u00f5es Exteriores para a Coopera\\u00e7\\u00e3o Internacional e Comunidades Angolanas adiantou que a coopera\\u00e7\\u00e3o visa, essencialmente, a troca de experi\\u00eancias e a melhoria do n\\u00edvel de organiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o interna, tendo em conta as val\\u00eancias que a Hungria pode oferecer no dom\\u00ednio da preven\\u00e7\\u00e3o e combate \\u00e0 criminalidade em todas as suas formas e manifesta\\u00e7\\u00f5es.<\\/p><p class=\\\"ql-align-justify\\\">A coopera\\u00e7\\u00e3o, prosseguiu Domingos Vieira Lopes, citado pelo <em>Jornal de Angola<\\/em>, abrange as \\u00e1reas de combate ao terrorismo, imigra\\u00e7\\u00e3o ilegal, corrup\\u00e7\\u00e3o, branqueamento de capitais, estendendo-se \\u00e0 forma\\u00e7\\u00e3o de quadros, fornecimento de equipamentos e consagra a presta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de assist\\u00eancia m\\u00fatua sobre as mat\\u00e9rias previstas no acordo, com destaque para a investiga\\u00e7\\u00e3o criminal.<\\/p><p>De acordo com o respons\\u00e1vel do MIREX, a assinatura deste instrumento jur\\u00eddico insere -se na busca de diversifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o de parcerias com vista a alcan\\u00e7ar e aprimorar as melhores formas, pr\\u00e1ticas e procedimentos na preven\\u00e7\\u00e3o e combate aos v\\u00e1rios crimes. O acordo, disse, vai permitir \\u00e0s partes refor\\u00e7arem a coopera\\u00e7\\u00e3o no dom\\u00ednio da seguran\\u00e7a e ordem p\\u00fablica, bem como potenciar os diferentes \\u00f3rg\\u00e3os e servi\\u00e7os executivos centrais do Minist\\u00e9rio do Interior com mais val\\u00eancias neste dom\\u00ednio que servir\\u00e1 para melhorar o exerc\\u00edcio da actividade quotidiana, a fim de elevar a qualidade do servi\\u00e7o p\\u00fablico prestado aos cidad\\u00e3os.<\\/p><p class=\\\"ql-align-justify\\\">| <strong>Fonte: <em>Jornal de Angola<\\/em>, edi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 27 de Abril.<\\/strong><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"}', 'assets/embaixada/img/paginas/5ec91c09a88a6cff0d94c3fb90e1e0c6b0dbf73c.jpg', 'pt-br', '2021-04-27 12:27:31', '2021-05-02 01:12:31', '1'),
(5, 80, 'Cultura angolana na Hungria', 'cultura-angolana-na-hungria', '{\"en\":\"Angolan culture present at CPLP party in Budapest\",\"hr\":\"Angol kult\\u00fara jelen van a budapesti CPLP bulin\",\"pt-br\":\"Cultura angolana na festa da CPLP em Budapeste\"}', '{\"en\":\"Portuguese Language Day also served to present Angolan cultural flavors in Hungary.\",\"hr\":\"A portug\\u00e1l nyelv napja az angolai kultur\\u00e1lis \\u00edzek bemutat\\u00e1s\\u00e1t is szolg\\u00e1lta Magyarorsz\\u00e1gon.\",\"pt-br\":\"O Dia da L\\u00edngua Portuguesa serviu tamb\\u00e9m para a apresenta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de sabores culturais angolanos na Hungria.\"}', '{\"en\":\"<p>Gastronomy, dance and the influence of linguistic particularities on cultural processes were the subjects with which the country performed in Hungary, this Wednesday (May 5), during the virtual ceremony held by the Embassies of the Republic of Angola, Brazil, Portugal and the Honorary Consulate of Cape Verde, within the scope of the celebrations of the Portuguese Language and Culture Day in the Community of Portuguese Speaking Countries (CPLP).<\\/p><p>In addition to disseminating and strengthening the presence of the Portuguese language in Hungary, this edition also served for the members of the CPLP Group in Budapest to showcase their cultural singularities, an occasion that Angola used to bring to the attention of the Hungarian public, and not only, one of the most well-known dishes of Angolan cuisine, <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/pt.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Calulu\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">calulu<\\/a>. From Luanda and in live format, chef Anabela Fran\\u00e7a, on behalf of Rua 11 Restaurant, has demonstrated this gastronomic specialty and its desserts, including a dessert based on <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.google.com\\/search?q=mucua&amp;rlz=1C1CHZL_pt-PTAO846AO846&amp;oq=mucua&amp;aqs=chrome..69i57j0l7j0i10j0.4890j0j7&amp;sourceid=chrome&amp;ie=UTF-8\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">mucua<\\/a>, which aroused the interest and curiosity of viewers in the national cuisine.<\\/p><p>Another theme that deserved to be highlighted was the evolution of Angolan dance, presented by choreographer and teacher Pedro Vieira Dias Tom\\u00e1s \\u201cMestre Petchu\\u201d, Ballet Tradicional Kilandukilu member, who made a historic incursion from Massemba to Kizomba, and with live demonstrations. In turn, the academic and poet Abreu Paxe presented the theme related to the Portuguese language in Angola, and how its specificity intervenes in the various forms of communication of cultural processes and objects, as well as in the most varied artistic processes and practices.<\\/p><p>It should also be noted that, among the countries of the Group, it was up to Angola to display a brief documentary regarding the Covid-19 pandemic and its management, presented by the Angolan Minister of Health, S\\u00edlvia Lutucuta, which will be available on the Vimeo platform until the end of Sunday, 9th May.<\\/p><p>Under the motto \\u201cInterculturality and mutual cultural influences\\u201d, the four CPLP countries with diplomatic representations in Hungary celebrated the event linked to the language that unites them, with the participation of a vast virtual audience, due to the current pandemic situation, composed of people from around the world interested in the history, culture, and literature of these countries.<\\/p><p>The 5th of May was established as the Portuguese Language and Culture Day at CPLP by the XIV Ordinary Meeting of the Council of Ministers of this organisation, which took place on 20th July 2009, and was recognised as World Day of the Portuguese Language on 25th November 2019, at the 40th session of the General Conference of the United Nations Educational, Scientific and Cultural Organisation (UNESCO).<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\",\"hr\":\"<p>A gasztron\\u00f3mia, a t\\u00e1nc \\u00e9s a nyelvi saj\\u00e1toss\\u00e1gok kultur\\u00e1lis folyamatokra gyakorolt \\u200b\\u200bhat\\u00e1sa volt az a t\\u00e9ma, amellyel az orsz\\u00e1g ezen a szerd\\u00e1n (m\\u00e1jus 5-\\u00e9n) fell\\u00e9pett Magyarorsz\\u00e1gon az Angolai K\\u00f6zt\\u00e1rsas\\u00e1g, Braz\\u00edlia, Portug\\u00e1lia nagyk\\u00f6vets\\u00e9gei \\u00e9s a tiszteletbeli Z\\u00f6ld-foki-szigeteki konzul\\u00e1tus, a Portug\\u00e1l Nyelv \\u00e9s Kult\\u00fara Napj\\u00e1nak a portug\\u00e1l nyelv\\u0171 orsz\\u00e1gok k\\u00f6z\\u00f6ss\\u00e9g\\u00e9ben (CPLP) tartott \\u00fcnneps\\u00e9gei keret\\u00e9ben.<\\/p><p>A portug\\u00e1l nyelv magyarorsz\\u00e1gi jelenl\\u00e9t\\u00e9nek terjeszt\\u00e9se \\u00e9s meger\\u0151s\\u00edt\\u00e9se mellett ez a kiad\\u00e1s a CPLP csoport budapesti tagjai sz\\u00e1m\\u00e1ra is bemutatta kultur\\u00e1lis saj\\u00e1toss\\u00e1gaikat, egy olyan alkalmat, amelyet Angola szokott felh\\u00edvni a magyar k\\u00f6zv\\u00e9lem\\u00e9ny figyelm\\u00e9re, \\u00e9s nemcsak az angolai konyha egyik legismertebb \\u00e9tele, a calulu. Luand\\u00e1b\\u00f3l \\u00e9s \\u00e9l\\u0151 form\\u00e1tumban Anabela Fran\\u00e7a s\\u00e9f a Rua 11 Restaurant nev\\u00e9ben bemutatta ezt a gasztron\\u00f3miai k\\u00fcl\\u00f6nlegess\\u00e9get \\u00e9s annak desszertjeit, k\\u00f6zt\\u00fck egy ny\\u00e1kalap\\u00fa desszertet, amely felkeltette a n\\u00e9z\\u0151k \\u00e9rdekl\\u0151d\\u00e9s\\u00e9t \\u00e9s k\\u00edv\\u00e1ncsis\\u00e1g\\u00e1t a nemzeti konyha ir\\u00e1nt.<\\/p><p>Egy m\\u00e1sik kiemel\\u00e9sre m\\u00e9lt\\u00f3 t\\u00e9ma az angolai t\\u00e1nc evol\\u00faci\\u00f3ja volt, koreogr\\u00e1fus \\u00e9s tan\\u00e1r Pedro Vieira Dias Tom\\u00e1s \\u201eMestre Petchu\\u201d, a Ballet Tradicional Kilandukilu tagja, aki Massemba \\u00e9s Kizomba k\\u00f6z\\u00f6tt t\\u00f6rt\\u00e9nelmi bet\\u00f6r\\u00e9st mutatott be, \\u00e9s \\u00e9l\\u0151 bemutat\\u00f3kkal. Viszont Abreu Paxe akad\\u00e9mikus \\u00e9s k\\u00f6lt\\u0151 Angol\\u00e1ban bemutatta a portug\\u00e1l nyelvvel kapcsolatos t\\u00e9m\\u00e1t, valamint azt, hogy saj\\u00e1toss\\u00e1ga hogyan avatkozik be a kultur\\u00e1lis folyamatok \\u00e9s t\\u00e1rgyak k\\u00fcl\\u00f6nb\\u00f6z\\u0151 kommunik\\u00e1ci\\u00f3s form\\u00e1iba, valamint a legv\\u00e1ltozatosabb m\\u0171v\\u00e9szeti folyamatokba \\u00e9s gyakorlatokba.<\\/p><p>Azt is meg kell jegyezni, hogy a csoport orsz\\u00e1gai k\\u00f6z\\u00fcl Angol\\u00e1nak kellett felmutatnia a Covid-19 j\\u00e1rv\\u00e1nyr\\u00f3l \\u00e9s annak kezel\\u00e9s\\u00e9r\\u0151l sz\\u00f3l\\u00f3 r\\u00f6vid dokumentumfilmet, amelyet S\\u00edlvia Lutucuta angolai eg\\u00e9szs\\u00e9g\\u00fcgyi miniszter mutatott be, \\u00e9s amely a Vimeo platformot m\\u00e1jus 9., vas\\u00e1rnap v\\u00e9g\\u00e9ig.<\\/p><p>Az \\u201eInterkulturalit\\u00e1s \\u00e9s k\\u00f6lcs\\u00f6n\\u00f6s kultur\\u00e1lis hat\\u00e1sok\\u201d mott\\u00f3 alatt a n\\u00e9gy diplom\\u00e1ciai k\\u00e9pviselettel rendelkez\\u0151 CPLP orsz\\u00e1g Magyarorsz\\u00e1gon meg\\u00fcnnepelte az \\u0151ket \\u00f6sszek\\u00f6t\\u0151 nyelvhez kapcsol\\u00f3d\\u00f3 esem\\u00e9nyt, a virtu\\u00e1lis k\\u00f6z\\u00f6ns\\u00e9g r\\u00e9szv\\u00e9tel\\u00e9vel, a jelenlegi pand\\u00e9mi\\u00e1s helyzet miatt a vil\\u00e1g minden t\\u00e1j\\u00e1r\\u00f3l \\u00e9rdekl\\u0151dik ezen orsz\\u00e1gok t\\u00f6rt\\u00e9nete, kult\\u00far\\u00e1ja \\u00e9s irodalma ir\\u00e1nt.<\\/p><p>M\\u00e1jus 5-\\u00e9t a CPLP portug\\u00e1l nyelv \\u00e9s kult\\u00fara napjak\\u00e9nt a szervezet Minisztertan\\u00e1cs\\u00e1nak XIV. Rendes \\u00fcl\\u00e9se 2009. j\\u00falius 20-\\u00e1n tartotta, amelyet november 25-\\u00e9n a portug\\u00e1l nyelv vil\\u00e1gnapj\\u00e1nak ismertek el. 2019, az ENSZ Oktat\\u00e1si, Tudom\\u00e1nyos \\u00e9s Kultur\\u00e1lis Szervezet\\u00e9nek (UNESCO) \\u00c1ltal\\u00e1nos Konferenci\\u00e1j\\u00e1nak 40. \\u00fcl\\u00e9sszak\\u00e1n.<\\/p>\",\"pt-br\":\"<p>A gastronomia, a dan\\u00e7a e a influ\\u00eancia das particularidades lingu\\u00edsticas nos processos culturais foram as mat\\u00e9rias com que o Pa\\u00eds se apresentou na Hungria, nesta quarta-feira (5), durante a cerim\\u00f3nia virtual realizada pelas Embaixadas da Rep\\u00fablica de Angola, Brasil, Portugal e o Consulado Honor\\u00e1rio de Cabo Verde, no \\u00e2mbito das celebra\\u00e7\\u00f5es do Dia da L\\u00edngua Portuguesa e da Cultura na Comunidade dos Pa\\u00edses de L\\u00edngua Portuguesa (CPLP).<\\/p><p>Para al\\u00e9m de divulgar e fortalecer a presen\\u00e7a da L\\u00edngua Portuguesa naquele pa\\u00eds da Europa Central, a edi\\u00e7\\u00e3o deste ano serviu igualmente para os membros do Grupo da CPLP em Budapeste exibirem as suas singularidades culturais, uma ocasi\\u00e3o aproveitada por Angola para levar ao conhecimento do p\\u00fablico h\\u00fangaro, e n\\u00e3o s\\u00f3, um dos pratos mais conhecidos da culin\\u00e1ria angolana, o calulu. A partir de Luanda e em formato <em>live<\\/em>, a <em>chef <\\/em>Anabela Fran\\u00e7a, do Restaurante Rua 11, demonstrou a confec\\u00e7\\u00e3o dessa especialidade gastron\\u00f3mica e os respectivos acompanhantes, incluindo uma sobremesa \\u00e0 base de m\\u00facua, tendo despertado o interesse e a curiosidade dos espectadores pela culin\\u00e1ria nacional.<\\/p><p>Um outro tema que mereceu destaque foi a evolu\\u00e7\\u00e3o da dan\\u00e7a angolana, apresentada pelo core\\u00f3grafo e professor Pedro Vieira Dias Tom\\u00e1s \\u201cMestre Petchu\\u201d, do Ballet Tradicional Kilandukilu, que fez uma incurs\\u00e3o hist\\u00f3rica da Massemba at\\u00e9 \\u00e0 Kizomba, e com demonstra\\u00e7\\u00f5es ao vivo. Por seu turno, o acad\\u00e9mico e poeta Abreu Paxe abordou a tem\\u00e1tica relacionada com a L\\u00edngua Portuguesa em Angola e como a sua especificidade interv\\u00e9m nas diversas formas de comunica\\u00e7\\u00e3o dos processos e objectos culturais, assim como nos mais variados processos e pr\\u00e1ticas art\\u00edsticas.<\\/p><p>Realce-se ainda que, de entre os pa\\u00edses do referido Grupo, coube a Angola a exibi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de um breve document\\u00e1rio sobre a pandemia da Covid-19 e a sua gest\\u00e3o, apresentado pela Ministra da Sa\\u00fade, S\\u00edlvia Lutucuta, que estar\\u00e1 dispon\\u00edvel na plataforma Vimeo at\\u00e9 ao final de domingo, dia 9 de Maio.<\\/p><p>Sob o lema \\u201c<em>Interculturalidade e influ\\u00eancias culturais m\\u00fatuas<\\/em>\\u201d, os quatro pa\\u00edses da CPLP com representa\\u00e7\\u00f5es diplom\\u00e1ticas na Hungria celebraram a efem\\u00e9ride ligada ao idioma que os une, contando com a participa\\u00e7\\u00e3o de um vasto audit\\u00f3rio virtual, devido \\u00e0 actual situa\\u00e7\\u00e3o pand\\u00e9mica, constitu\\u00eddo por pessoas de v\\u00e1rios pontos do mundo interessados na hist\\u00f3ria, cultura e literatura desses pa\\u00edses.<\\/p><p>O 5 de Maio foi institu\\u00eddo como Dia da L\\u00edngua Portuguesa e da Cultura na CPLP pela XIV Reuni\\u00e3o Ordin\\u00e1ria do Conselho de Ministros desta organiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o, decorrida a 20 de Julho de 2009, e foi reconhecido como Dia Mundial da L\\u00edngua Portuguesa a 25 de Novembro de 2019, na 40.\\u00aa sess\\u00e3o da Confer\\u00eancia Geral da Organiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o das Na\\u00e7\\u00f5es Unidas para a Educa\\u00e7\\u00e3o, Ci\\u00eancia e Cultura (UNESCO).<\\/p><p>| Embaixada da Rep\\u00fablica de Angola na Hungria<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\"}', 'assets/embaixada/img/paginas/91bd261f4728eaa3bf74c1190c8fca09ce33a179.jpg', 'pt-br', '2021-05-09 02:15:02', '2021-05-09 05:33:20', '1');

